        {
            "title": "聯準會Hammack:利率「將在相當長時間內維持不變」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8uWFVPeORr9rf4z5xkDehA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/Brazil-Stock-Market_3_M_1440048532.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"聯準會\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:聯準會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯準會\">聯準會</a>克里夫蘭聯邦儲備銀行總裁Beth <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Hammack\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Hammack;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Hammack\">Hammack</a>週三表示,目前利率水準適當,央行可能會在一段時間內維持不變,不過她承認風險可能會推動政策朝任一方向調整。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hammack在CNBC上表示:「我認為利率處於良好水準。」「我的基本預期是,我們將在相當長時間內維持不變,但我確實認為利率存在雙向風險。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hammack指出,未來的政策調整可能會朝任一方向發展,取決於即將公布的經濟數據。她說:「根據數據表現,我們可能需要更寬鬆或更緊縮的政策,這都是有風險的。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-66033912-d2cd-3252-97c4-85359d6a22b7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位克里夫蘭聯準會總裁強調能源價格是需要關注的關鍵因素,表示高能源成本可能既會推升通膨,也會拖累經濟成長。她強調,能源價格上漲的持續時間和幅度將是決定其經濟影響的關鍵因素。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hammack表示,就業市場似乎相當平衡,目前並未構成通膨壓力來源。她補充說,通膨預期看起來相當受控,儘管她指出聯準會已經連續五年未能達成通膨目標,消費者也面臨了長期的高通膨環境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hammack說:「供給衝擊對貨幣政策來說很棘手。」她形容當前環境對聯準會決策而言是一個艱難時期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在其他議題上,Hammack表示,人工智慧將對經濟產生何種影響仍不明朗。她也強調聯準會獨立性的重要性,並表示在央行面臨威脅的情況下,她專注於做好自己的工作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E6%BA%96%E6%9C%83hammack-%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87-%E5%B0%87%E5%9C%A8%E7%9B%B8%E7%95%B6%E9%95%B7%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E5%85%A7%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A-135927542.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-15 23:02:11",
